column5: well as you can see its tinbangers B-day today  , hope u have a good one dad.
HEY!!!!!! Have a good one Bud!
Hey, happy birthday Dave!  We didn't make it out on the ice this winter, maybe we'll get out on the open water once the ice is fully out and the seasons start opening.  Mike
They sure do, me thinks I,ll buy him a coffee.  Have a great day.
Hey Dave, hope you have a great day...  Maureen
Dave  Have a great B day  John
All the "Best" on this day to you and may you have many many more....
All the best Dave...would you like a coffee with your cake?
Happy Birthday Dave. Hope your having a good one.
